                  , and in the Dwelling-House of the said Tbo. Scales
            </rs>. Mr. Scales depos'd, That he had lost at several Times, a considerable Quantity of Lead, and after the Prisoner had been melting, he found some Ladles full had in the Sand.</p>
               <p>His Confession was read in Court, in which he own'd, he had at several Times given of his Master's Lead to one 
               <persName id="t17281016-11-person84">
                  James 
                  Brooks 
