             had for the said Lead. That he had given Brooks in all about seven hundred Weight. This Confession being sign'd with his own Hand, and it appearing that he did it voluntarily, without either Menaces, Threats, or Promises, the Jury found him <rs id="t17281016-11-verdict52" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17281016-11-verdict52" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
